<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-55f8ebc805e65b5b71ddafdae390e3be2bcd69af">Description</h2>
<em>Class++ is a module that adds 11 new classes to standard ToME. The new classes' goals are threefold:</em> 
    <ol type="1">

    <li>
<p>
<em>Increase the representation of certain superclasses: Archer and Rogue each have five class selections.</em> 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
<em>Increase the usage of nearly useless item types, namely essences, runes, and trapping kits.</em> 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
<em>Add a few cool powers and stretch the limits of the Engine.</em> 
</p>
</li>

    </ol>


<p>
This partial release was made because I wanted to let everyone know that I'm still working on this module, it's just that things have gotten busy lately. Assimilators have most of their powers now, and you can play one if you want to see them in action. A thanks.txt file was added as well. This version is not packaged with any characters. 
</p>
